If Certbot fails

The most common causes are:

Port 80 isn't reachable from the internet.
Another service is using port 80.
The domain doesn't point to your server.

You can check that Nginx is listening on both ports with:

sudo ss -tlnp | grep nginx

Expected output:

0.0.0.0:80
0.0.0.0:443

(Port 443 will appear after the certificate is installed.)

